Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混蛋是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…冰結君?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,危險  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住手  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你才該放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放手  放手啊  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,放手  放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼莫名其妙哭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼襲擊我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我被救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被那人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我照著那人告訴我的去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  這傢伙交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
